    <Step id="e71bbd8c-34d3-4216-a5af-2d5a9a5d9139" name="Everyone has a responsibility to report safeguarding concerns" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;All people who work with or have contact with adults at risk need to be alert to the possibility of abuse and should be able to share their concerns with appropriate people within their own agency or establishment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;It is essential that all staff accept that the abuse of adults at risk does unfortunately occur. No suspiction of abuse should ever be ignored.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;Staff may become aware of possible abuse when they:-&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;witness an abusive act  &lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='1'&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;are told about abuse by someone else  &lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='1'&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;are told about abuse by the service user  &lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='1'&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;find evidence of abuse  &lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='00' leftmargin='1'&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Arial' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;recognise several of the abuse indicators and become concerned.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" intro="true">
